00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:38,340
Sure.

590
00:30:38,533 --> 00:30:39,860
Let's go somewhere else.

591
00:30:58,300 --> 00:30:59,260
Your coffees.

592
00:31:01,340 --> 00:31:02,180
This one is yours.

593
00:31:04,066 --> 00:31:05,100
Light roast Americano.

594
00:31:11,190 --> 00:31:11,580
I...

