657
00:35:43,140 --> 00:35:43,830
You know what?

658
00:35:43,830 --> 00:35:44,670
If you try to explain

659
00:35:44,870 --> 00:35:45,700
how your system

660
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:46,310
perfectly fits

661
