I'll do most of the talking.

679
00:36:20,020 --> 00:36:20,860
Relax.

680
00:36:23,830 --> 00:36:24,790
We're here.

681
00:36:24,790 --> 00:36:25,700
Sorry.

682
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:26,580
