764
00:39:05,100 --> 00:39:06,580
It has plenty of space,

765
00:39:06,950 --> 00:39:07,950
and no one lives here.

766
00:39:07,950 --> 00:39:09,390
Just put it here,

767
00:39:09,390 --> 00:39:10,230
